      <abstract encodinganalog="5203_">The collection contains photographs of
		  newspaper owner Charles Samuel Jackson of Pendleton and Portland, Or., his
		  family, and his newspaper enterprises, including the <emph render="italic">East
		  Oregonian</emph> and <emph render="italic">Oregon Journal</emph>.</abstract>
